  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Whether through uncanny reflexes, remarkable luck, gengineered skin fibers, or subtle telekinetic shielding, you have natural defenses equivalent to high-quality combat armor. The benefits of this focus don&rsquo;t stack with armor, though Dexterity or shield modifiers apply.</p><p><strong>Level 1:</strong> You have an innate Armor Class of 15 plus half your character level, rounded up.</p><p><strong>Level 2:</strong> Your abilities are so effective that they render you immune to unarmed attacks or primitive weaponry as if you wore powered armor.</p>",
